<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Attention: A Work Order has been removed.</title>
        <style type="text/css">
            body {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                min-width: 100%;
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 1.5;
                background-color: #FAFAFA;
                color: #222222;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
                font-weight: 700;
                line-height: 1.25;
                margin-top: 0;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            p {
                margin-top: 0;
                margin-bottom: 24px;
            }

            table td{
            vertical-align: top;
            }

            .email-wrapper{
                max-width:700px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }

            .email-header{
                background-color: darkgreen;
                padding: 24px;
                color: #fff;
            }

            .email-body{
                padding:24px;
                background-color: #f6f6f6;
            }
            .email-footer{
                background-color: #f6f6f6;
                padding: 24px;
            }

        </style>
        <body>
            <div class="email-wrapper">

                <div class="email-header">
                    <h1>Deleted Work Order</h1>
                </div>
                
                <div class="email-body">
                <p>Hello, you have a work order request that has been deleted. Below are the details.</p>
                <p>Work Order Number: <%= workOrderNumber %></p>
                <p>Description: <%= description %></p>
                <p>Priority: <%= priority %></p>
                <p>Status: <%= status %></p>
                <p>Service Type: <%= serviceType %></p>
                <p>Category: <%= categoryTitle %></p>
                <p>Location: <%= locationTitles %></p>
                <p>Deleted By: <%= username %></p>
                </div>    
                <div class="email-footer">
                    <p>Holiday Inn Work Order System - All rights reserved.</p>
                </div>
            </div>   
        </body>
    </head>
</html>